Uses of Package
org.flemil.util

Packages that use org.flemil.util
org.flemil.control This package contains classes that play a role in the control of the application as a whole. 
org.flemil.ui This package contains interfaces that represent the collective properties for components that can be displayed on the screen. 
org.flemil.ui.component This package contains the actual implementation of items that can be shown on a display. 
org.flemil.util This package contains classes that provide utility function for the application such as gradient images generation, rectangular areas of display representation and more. 
 

Classes in org.flemil.util used by org.flemil.control

          Class that provides utility methods such as resizing for manipulating images to be used for display as well as creation of images to be used for gradients in the applications UI generation.
